						               													<description>This is the 5th expansion for the base-game Alhambra. It was presented at the Essen gamefair Spiel '08.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As in all the other expansions, this one contains 4 new modules.&amp;#10;They are as follows:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-Die Karawanserei (the Caravan). Cards and markers.&amp;#10;These special cards can be taken. Every turn you may increase the indicated amount of money on the card and use it to buy buildings.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-Die K&amp;uuml;nste der Mauren (the art of the Moorish). Tiles.&amp;#10;With these tiles you can get extra points for the amount of buildings you have of the same value.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-Die Macht des Sultans (the power of the sultan). Cards and a die.&amp;#10;You can buy the card for 7 of the indicated color. Then you roll the die and mark the building on the card. When a new building of that color is added to the building site, you can take it, even if it is not your turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-Die neuen Wertungsk&amp;auml;rtchen (the new valuation cards). Tiles.&amp;#10;At the beginning of the game you draw 3 tiles that show different ranking orders for the buildings for the three valuations.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Expands:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Alhambra&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
